HEADWORD: Mora
<hw>Mo"ra</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.]</ety> <fld>(Rom. & Civil
Law)</fld> <def>Delay; esp., culpable delay; postponement.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Moraine</ent>⟦br⟧
